### Test 1: Get default message
GET http://localhost:8888/api/v1/chat

### Test 2: Get message with custom prompt
GET http://localhost:8888/api/v1/chat?message=Who are you?

### Test 3: Ask a question
GET http://localhost:8888/api/v1/chat?message=What is the capital of France?

### Test 4: Another question
GET http://localhost:8888/api/v1/chat?message=What is 2 + 2?

### Test 5: Creative prompt
GET http://localhost:8888/api/v1/chat?message=Tell me a joke

### Test 6: Stream - custom prompt
GET http://localhost:8888/api/v1/chat/stream?message=Tell me a short story about a dragon
Accept: text/event-stream

### Test 7: Stream - another creative prompt
GET http://localhost:8888/api/v1/chat/stream?message=Write a poem about the ocean
Accept: text/event-stream

### Test 8: Stream - technical question
GET http://localhost:8888/api/v1/chat/stream?message=How does machine learning work?
Accept: text/event-stream

### Test 9: Stream - default message
GET http://localhost:8888/api/v1/chat/stream
Accept: text/event-stream


#### Test 10: Stream - ollama chat
GET http://localhost:8888/api/v1/ollama/chat?message=Почему нельзя обновлять сразу много записей?

#### Test 11: Stream - ollama chat stream
GET http://localhost:8888/api/v1/ollama/chat/stream?message=Почему нельзя обновлять сразу много записей?
Accept: text/event-stream

#### Test 12: Ollama embed
GET http://localhost:8888/api/v1/ollama/embed?input=Почему нельзя обновлять сразу много записей?

#### Test 13: Stream - ollama embed async
GET http://localhost:8888/api/v1/ollama/embed/async?input=Почему нельзя обновлять сразу много записей?
Accept: text/event-stream

#### Test 10: Stream - ollama embed
GET http://localhost:8888/api/v1/ollama/chat/message=Почему нельзя обновлять сразу много записей?


